4) Security Groups

Public EC2 SG (sg-public)
Inbound:
SSH (22) from your IP only
HTTP (80) from your IP (or 0.0.0.0/0 if youâ€™ll host a test web page)
Outbound: allow all

Private EC2 SG (sg-private)
Inbound:
SSH (22) from sg-public (reference the SG)
Outbound: allow all



5) EC2 Instances

